query:
SELECT
                id                     AS "id!: Uuid",
                org_id                 AS "org_id!: Uuid",
                provider_name          AS "provider_name!: String",
                decrypted_provider_key AS "provider_key!: Secret<String>"
            FROM decrypted_provider_keys
            WHERE org_id = $1
              AND provider_name = $2
            LIMIT 1
